<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Parcel Status Update</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Hello <%= senderName %>,</h2>
    <p>The status of the parcel you sent titled <strong><%= title %></strong> has been updated.</p>
    <p><strong>New Status:</strong> <%= status %></p>
    <p>We'll notify the receiver and keep you updated too.</p>
    <p>Thanks for using <strong>SendIt</strong>!</p>
  </body>
</html>
